{"name":"Hound","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Having your suspect in your sights, you cannot let them escape. As part of the check you substituted your Devise a Stratagem roll for, you can Stride to put your foe in your reach. If you do, you must end your movement closer to the target of your Devise a Stratagem.</p>\n<p>If you have an appropriate Speed, you can Burrow, Climb, Fly, or Swim instead of Striding.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["hb_complication","investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"domain":"attack-roll","key":"RollOption","option":"complicationActive","toggleable":true},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Complication","slug":"complication-penalty","selector":"attack-roll","value":-2,"predicate":["devise-a-stratagem","complicationActive"]}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664794909163,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"2bziwyREwacUhwqx"}
{"name":"Anticipate Assault","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You suspect that you may be goaded into a trap if you attack now, so you instead shore up your defences. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your AC against the target of your Devise a Stratagem.</p>\n<p><strong>Turnabout</strong> The bonus is +2 instead.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-investigators-pnc.investigators-pnc-effects.a8IYJkuLSN4hdhV0]{Effect: Anticipate Assault}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["investigator","hb_pivot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:35:03.851+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.r8WUndnTXBeVxtLb"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664782503854,"modifiedTime":1664784659509,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"2rIDMP6h2TQNd345"}
{"name":"Strategic Draw","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>While on the case, you cannot be caught unawares. As part of the check you substituted your Devise a Stratagem roll for, you Interact to draw a weapon.</p>\n<p>This feat serves as Quick Draw for the purposes of meeting prerequisites.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["hb_complication","investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"domain":"attack-roll","key":"RollOption","option":"complicationActive","toggleable":true},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Complication","selector":"attack-roll","slug":"complication-penalty","value":-2,"predicate":["devise-a-stratagem","complicationActive"]}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664795063893,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"4BCqLO58gHaUnn5l"}
{"name":"One By One","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong> An enemy you have a temporary lead on from @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-investigators-pnc.investigators-pnc-feats.y0zNlrBLCXixls5I]{Guilt By Association} is reduced to 0 Hit Points.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Having struck at the weakest link in your enemy&rsquo;s numbers, you move along the proverbial chain. You end your temporary lead from Guilt By Association, returning to your original lead, then as a free action take the Guilt By Association action against another foe in the encounter. This foe must still fulfil the conditions set by Guilt By Association, and it must also be connected to the target of your original lead.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T12:53:04.991+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":10},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Guilt By Association"}]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"day"}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.01goZGpE04aDtqvo"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664794384996,"modifiedTime":1664794502436,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Dl4DbvNzDZSgpkf5"}
{"name":"Wrong Man In The Right Place","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The plan you put into action is sound, but you're out of position -- thankfully, your ally isn't. Choose an ally within 30 feet of you. That ally may gain the result of your Devise a Stratagem roll as you share your strategy with them. If you use gestures to share your strategy, this action gains the manipulate trait. If you use words, it gains the auditory and linguistic trait.</p>\n<p>If they accept, they are bound by the same restrictions as you would be after you Devised a Stratagem: the next time they Strike the creature you've chosen for your Devise a Stratagem later this round, they must use the result of your Devise a Stratagem roll for their Strike's attack roll instead of rolling. They don't get to add your or their Intelligence modifier to the attack roll, nor do they gain any benefits associated with your Devise a Stratagem substitutions, like Strategic Strike.</p>\n<p>Whether they accept your Devise a Stratagem roll or not, they become temporarily immune to your Wrong Man in the Right Place for 10 minutes.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-investigators-pnc.investigators-pnc-effects.GGI2cSMAqAhoxoGH]{Effect: Wrong Man In the Right Place Immunity}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["investigator","hb_pivot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:35:03.851+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":12},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ePhvdDpKyXomLiqy"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.3.2","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1664782503854,"modifiedTime":1667160044033,"lastModifiedBy":"id72NUpnWPhqEYN2"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Dy6QGFUDCHs5TYz6"}
{"name":"Reflexive Reload","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Seeing the opportunity present itself, you prepare your weapon with blinding speed to make the winning shot. As part of the check you substituted your Devise a Stratagem roll for, you Interact to Reload a weapon you're holding.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["hb_complication","investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"domain":"attack-roll","key":"RollOption","option":"complicationActive","toggleable":true},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Complication","selector":"attack-roll","slug":"complication-penalty","value":-2,"predicate":["devise-a-stratagem","complicationActive"]}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664794904766,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"KQIgzyYxZhwoGRXM"}
{"name":"Strategic Spellslinger","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>As you pursued your magical studies, you realised that even magic follows certain patterns and logics. In addition to using Devise a Stratagem to modify a Strike, you can use it to modify a Cast a Spell attempt when casting a spell with the attack trait, substituting your Devise a Stratagem roll for the spell attack roll. You must apply the substitution to the first eligible action you make, whether it&rsquo;s a Strike, an Athletics action (if you have the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Tu1hOEr6Ko9Df54L]{Athletic Strategist} investigator feat), or a spell attack roll.</p>\n<p>You can also use your Intelligence modifier instead of the spell&rsquo;s spellcasting modifier for the spell attack roll, though you may not add the additional precision damage from Strategic Strike to your spell&rsquo;s damage.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"ability":"int","key":"FlatModifier","predicate":["class:investigator","devise-a-stratagem"],"selector":"spell-attack-roll","type":"ability"}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T11:01:18.412+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"ability to cast spells"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rFf5v06MoMGHmEbZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664787678415,"modifiedTime":1664788377091,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Od1TvnI4myrkPBOq"}
{"name":"Fighting Words","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Sticks and stones may break their bones, but sometimes, a well-timed quip or a powerful statement can make all the difference. You make an Intimidation check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.2u915NdUyQan6uKF]{Demoralize} the target of your Devise a Stratagem. If you have the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.0GF2j54roPFIDmXf]{Bon Mot} skill feat, you can choose to do that instead.</p>\n<p><strong>Turnabout</strong> You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your attempt to Demoralise or Bon Mot.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-investigators-pnc.investigators-pnc-effects.YOIKav4tIaudurZm]{Effect: Fighting Words (Turnabout)}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["investigator","hb_pivot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:42:11.191+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7HX5HFoyyVKabKJQ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664782931196,"modifiedTime":1664783747612,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"QmPrnk1ZyhNW4L9B"}
{"name":"Minor Mystery","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>There are some cases that don&rsquo;t require your full attention, but are still good to keep track of. Once per day, you may Pursue a Lead even if you already have the maximum amount of active investigations ongoing by designating it as a minor lead. A minor lead lasts until 1 hour passes, after which it automatically ends.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"day"}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664786728978,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"TZbYTsy7RPPHQwBz"}
{"name":"Long Arm Of The Law","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When you make a Strike whose attack roll you substituted with your Devising a Stratagem roll, you may increase your reach for that Strike by 5 feet.</p>\n<p>If you have the Athletic Strategist investigator feat, and your weapon has the disarm, shove, or trip trait, you can increase your reach for the corresponding action instead of a Strike.</p>\n<p>If you have the Strategic Spellslinger investigator feat, you can increase the range of spells eligible for substition by Devise a Stratagem with a range of touch by 5 feet.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["hb_complication","investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"domain":"attack-roll","key":"RollOption","option":"complicationActive","toggleable":true},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Complication","slug":"complication-penalty","selector":"attack-roll","value":-2,"predicate":["devise-a-stratagem","complicationActive"]}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664798638935,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Wc2dpOaoaqEcj3J9"}
{"name":"Multilayered Gambit","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>When the opportunity presents itself, you don't just have one or two plans at the ready, but a dozen. You may apply two complications to a check whose roll you substituted your Devise a Stratagem roll with. If you do, you may ignore the penalty of one of these complications.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":20},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664802377222,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Z6ESSOPx8Y7hxrqe"}
{"name":"Calculated Strike","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You notice a telling weakness on your foe, and strike true at it with all your might. If you would apply Strategic Strike to a melee Strike, you add one additional die to its precision damage.</p>\n<p>The aforementioned Strike counts as two attacks for the purposes of calculating your multiple attack penalty.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-investigators-pnc.investigators-pnc-effects.UBt4GWu0KCzwpUMj]{Effect: Calculated Strike}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["hb_complication","investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"category":"precision","diceNumber":1,"dieSize":"d6","key":"DamageDice","predicate":["devise-a-stratagem","class-feature:strategic-strike","complicationActive"],"selector":"strike-damage"},{"domain":"attack-roll","key":"RollOption","option":"complicationActive","toggleable":true},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Complication","slug":"complication-penalty","selector":"attack-roll","value":-2,"predicate":["devise-a-stratagem","complicationActive"]}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T10:29:38.632+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"strategic strike"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3lya9HjahHJx42dq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664785778636,"modifiedTime":1664794887903,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"waAySpdXsi1jdsrM"}
{"name":"Guilt By Association","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You have a lead, and you are in an encounter.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Though you have no concrete evidence of any wrongdoing, you reason that your opponent must be suspicious if only due to their connection to the evidence you do have. Choose a creature who is connected in some way to one of the leads you have. You set aside that lead, but not end it, then Pursue a Lead against that creature. This temporary lead lasts until the encounter ends, after which you return to your original lead. This temporary lead cannot be set aside, thus you cannot swap it out with another Guilt By Association or the Suspect of Opportunity feat.</p>\n<p>Examples of valid connections between your lead and the creature are as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>if the subject of your lead is a location, then a creature is connected if it is inside the location, or if it describes something of the location that you are aware should not be public knowledge &ndash; for example, a creature revealing that they know of a hidden room would count as connected to it.</li>\n<li>if the subject of your lead is an item, a creature wielding, wearing, or knowing something of the item that you are aware is not public knowledge would count as connected to it.</li>\n<li>if the subject of your lead is a creature, then another creature is connected if you are aware of any relationship between these two creatures. This relationship has to be deeper than mere acquaintances.</li>\n<li>in combat, if both the subject of your lead and another creature are fighting on the same side, you can reasonably suspect that they are connected.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ultimately, your GM is the final arbiter when it comes to determining valid connections.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Investigators: Pivots & Complications"},"traits":{"value":["concentrate","investigator"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-03T09:58:49.356+02:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":4},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":2},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"day"}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rP59727HoeIu8Xuq"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664783929359,"modifiedTime":1664794417670,"lastModifiedBy":"1nIvj2kghHEjRn0P"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"y0zNlrBLCXixls5I"}
